      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "忙しいところすまない\n次回のライブバトルについてなんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry to bother you while you’re busy.\nIt’s about the next live battle…",
