      "text": "……ランキング五位のグループとの対決を\n断った件……ですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…About how we turned down\nThe match against the fifth-ranked group… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "え？　あ、ああ……。よく分かったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Oh‚ yeah… How did you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.2736059029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
