      "text": "{user}さん、特に理由も聞かないで\n「そうか」としか言わなかったので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ you didn’t even ask why‚\nAnd you just said‚ “Okay.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
