      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……あれは正直、面を食らってしまってな\nどう答えたものやらって思ってさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… Honestly‚ I was caught off guard‚\nAnd I didn’t know what to say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "三人が決めたことなら……と一度は納得したが\nやっぱり、ちゃんと理由は聞いておきたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I accepted it at first‚ thinking… “If that’s what you three decided…”\nBut I still want to hear your reason properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.0666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.5494808989
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
