      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、瑠依達なら挑戦すると思っていたからな\n断った時の気持ちは、今も変わらないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ yeah‚ I thought you’d challenge them‚ Rui.\nDo you still feel the same way as when you turned it down?",
        "id": ""
